    "data": [
        {
            "title": "南首上樓書共提供313伙 部署短期內開示位",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/ade2c1165628adf9df548c4e7da664fd/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250213/_2025021317555844259.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>恒基九龍城南首今日正式上載樓書，恒基物業代理董事及營業(二)部總經理韓家輝表示，項目提供313個住宅單位。項目設開放式至兩房，戶型多元化，迎合不同家庭的需要，預計短期內開放示範單位予公眾參觀。\n\n</p>\n<p>其中開放式標準單位面積為200方呎，共40伙，佔約13%；1房標準單位面積則為258至263方呎，共178伙，佔約57%；2房標準單位面積則為342至351方呎，共78伙，佔約 25%。\n\n</p>\n<p>另設17伙開放式至2房的特色戶，佔約5%，包括平台特色戶佔15伙，面積為178至313方呎，連76至528方呎平台，而天際特色戶佔2伙，面積為353至358方呎，連182至187方呎平台。項目預計關鍵日期為2025年12月31日，距離至今不足11個月。項目設於尖沙咀美麗華廣場的示範單位及售樓處已完工，部署短期內開放。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2052608/即時-地產-南首上樓書共提供313伙-部署短期內開示位",
            "pub_date": "2025-02-13 18:01:07",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "深圳保安飲醉酒變「古惑仔」  飯店擸凳掃場數分鐘被刑拘︱有片",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/686e386/0x0/100/none/724775bb426067182608253a844e9c7b/2025-02/New_Project_4151542123.jpg\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/c0f3631de9ef71efbff72680f9ea0102/8eb4dcc0b6384e96ad99a2c0c60230b2-bb8ac3f290b0798235eb76225c247286-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67adc238b26d6\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67adc238b26d9\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"深圳有男保安酒後破壞飯店被刑拘。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/89b928b1cfb54ec8e87f4f6bb80a753d/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250213/_2025021317480865093.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">深圳有男保安酒後破壞飯店被刑拘。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>深圳有保安日前食醉後發酒癲，竟在一間飯店內大肆破壞數分鐘，擸起木凳瘋狂打砸店內物品，嚇得食客職員四散，店內被嚴重破壞，玻璃、碗筷、食物跌滿一地。涉事保安已因醉酒滋事被刑事拘留。\n\n</p><h2>破壞持續數分鐘無人敢阻止</h2>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"深圳有保安醉酒後瘋狂破壞飯店。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/435ecd88c7bc30e39a67dc6728444bf2/2025-02/4565656.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        深圳有保安醉酒後瘋狂破壞飯店。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"深圳有保安醉酒後瘋狂破壞飯店。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e098f23453b1989b44df76780c70dc29/2025-02/56156632.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        深圳有保安醉酒後瘋狂破壞飯店。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"深圳有保安醉酒後瘋狂破壞飯店。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/99bac91233169bd7f5ca6b2a15762209/2025-02/154456546.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        深圳有保安醉酒後瘋狂破壞飯店。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"深圳有保安醉酒後瘋狂破壞飯店。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e17536c4cdd3360aeb6b4decded0b312/2025-02/526562652.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        深圳有保安醉酒後瘋狂破壞飯店。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"深圳有保安醉酒後瘋狂破壞飯店。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a709b5b4b41e74c0c9daa93454ace2e8/2025-02/A_001_1.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        深圳有保安醉酒後瘋狂破壞飯店。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"深圳有保安醉酒後瘋狂破壞飯店。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8103d4d11b33bcf1c7b96f22e880b057/2025-02/A_002.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        深圳有保安醉酒後瘋狂破壞飯店。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3427520/%E6%9F%AC%E5%9F%94%E5%AF%A8%E8%A8%98%E8%80%85%E9%86%89%E9%85%92%E5%B8%B6%E5%8F%8D%E5%9D%A6%E5%85%8B%E5%9C%B0%E9%9B%B7%E9%97%96%E8%AD%A6%E5%B1%80-%E9%85%92%E9%86%92%E5%BE%8C%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E8%87%B4%E6%AD%89\">柬埔寨記者醉酒帶反坦克地雷闖警局 酒醒後公開致歉</a>\n</p>\n<p>據網上流傳影片及內媒消息，事件發生於11日晚，深圳龍華區一名穿保安制服男子，疑因飲醉酒發酒瘋，在一間飯店內不斷破壞，拿起木凳不斷打砸店內物品，店內桌子椅子被推翻，餐具食物散滿一地。\n\n</p>\n<p>由於醉保安狀態癲狂及手持「武器」，飯店職員及食客，無人敢上前阻止，打砸過程長達數分鐘，令飯店嚴重破壞，直至接報民警到場，拘捕涉事男保安。\n\n</p>\n<p>《南方都市報》13日報道，指從深圳公安了解到，涉事男保安已因醉酒滋事被依法刑事拘留。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2052605/即時-中國-深圳保安飲醉酒變-古惑仔-飯店擸凳掃場數分鐘被刑拘︱有片",
